<L>__{exterior worcester road. night.}
<A>__{at the top of the steps he stops for breath and he looks around. there is no sign of annie but he knows this street the worcester road a row of grey georgian houses, their backs against the hill, their sloping front gardens looking out over the rooftops of malvern. most of the street is in darkness but the house directly opposite has lights in the window. he knows this house also. he hesitates, then crosses the street towards it.}
